    },
    {
      "type": "TEXT",
      "id": "node_85",
      "name": "ps1",
      "x": 571,
      "y": 230,
      "width": 295,
      "content": "→ Outcome UI removes navigation in favour of direct goal completion",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "color": "#0E0E0E",
      "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Sans",
      "fontWeight": 400,
      "fontStyle": "normal",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "lineHeight": 1.6,
      "letterSpacing": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "TEXT",
      "id": "node_86",
      "name": "ps2",
      "x": 571,
      "y": 250,
      "width": 295,
      "content": "→ Designers now define frameworks, not screens",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "color": "#0E0E0E",
      "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Sans",
      "fontWeight": 400,
      "fontStyle": "normal",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "lineHeight": 1.6,
      "letterSpacing": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "TEXT",
      "id": "node_87",
      "name": "ps3",
      "x": 571,
      "y": 270,
      "width": 295,
      "content": "→ GenUI adoption fastest in health and finance apps",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "color": "#0E0E0E",
      "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Sans",
      "fontWeight": 400,
      "fontStyle": "normal",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "lineHeight": 1.6,
      "letterSpacing": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "TEXT",
      "id": "node_88",
      "name": "body-1",
      "x": 559,
      "y": 300,
      "width": 327,
      "content": "The first sign was subtle. In late 2025, several popular fintech apps quietly removed their navigation bars. Not as a design statement — because with AI routing context, users were arriving at the right place before they even thought to tap.",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "color": "#0E0E0E",
      "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Sans",
      "fontWeight": 400,
      "fontStyle": "normal",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "lineHeight": 1.75,
      "letterSpacing": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "RECTANGLE",
      "id": "node_89",
      "name": "hl-bg",
      "x": 559,
      "y": 394,
      "width": 327,
      "height": 54,
      "fill": "rgba(200,51,26,0.07)",
      "cornerRadius": 3,
      "strokeColor": null,
      "strokeWidth": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "RECTANGLE",
      "id": "node_90",
      "name": "hl-bar",
      "x": 559,
      "y": 394,
      "width": 3,
      "height": 54,
      "fill": "#C8331A",
      "cornerRadius": 1,
      "strokeColor": null,
      "strokeWidth": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "TEXT",
      "id": "node_91",
      "name": "hl-text",
      "x": 571,
      "y": 400,
      "width": 302,
      "content": "\"Interfaces are increasingly answering the question you were about to ask, rather than presenting options.\"",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "color": "#0E0E0E",
      "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Sans",
      "fontWeight": 400,
      "fontStyle": "italic",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "lineHeight": 1.65,
      "letterSpacing": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "TEXT",
      "id": "node_92",
      "name": "body-2",
      "x": 559,
      "y": 458,
      "width": 327,
      "content": "Researchers at NN/G found GenUI achieves 40% faster task completion versus conventional navigation — but at the cost of user understanding of the underlying system.",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "color": "#0E0E0E",
      "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Sans",
      "fontWeight": 400,
      "fontStyle": "normal",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "lineHeight": 1.75,
      "letterSpacing": 0
    },
